WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.710
Hello, young word explorer.

2
00:00:01.710 --> 00:00:05.129
Welcome to Unit 7, The World Around Us.

3
00:00:05.129 --> 00:00:09.403
This unit has 20 vocabulary cards in 4 learning groups.

4
00:00:09.403 --> 00:00:12.395
Group 1 is Caring for the Environment.

5
00:00:12.395 --> 00:00:17.096
Listen for words such as planting, watering, picking up, litter, recycling.

6
00:00:17.096 --> 00:00:20.088
Group 2 is Parts of a Plant.

7
00:00:20.088 --> 00:00:24.362
Listen for words such as roots, stem, leaves, flower, seeds.

8
00:00:24.362 --> 00:00:27.354
Group 3 is Nature and Our Planet.

9
00:00:27.354 --> 00:00:31.628
Listen for words such as tree, air, water, soil, Earth.

10
00:00:31.628 --> 00:00:35.902
Group 4 is Words for Saying Thank You to Nature.

11
00:00:35.902 --> 00:00:40.176
Listen for words such as glad, happy, thankful, appreciate, important.

12
00:00:40.176 --> 00:00:50.861
For each word, listen and repeat, read five sentences, notice the word type, practise spelling, write your own sentence, and ask the tutor for help.

13
00:00:50.861 --> 00:00:53.852
You are ready to begin Unit 7.
